{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0001", "text": "像突襲 平靜五臟裏 劇痛得彎腰流淚", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 2, 5, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoeng6", "dat6", "zaap6", "ping4", "zing6", "ng5", "zong6", "leoi5", "kek6", "tung3", "dak1", "waan1", "jiu1", "lau4", "leoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "突襲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "平靜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "五臟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "劇痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "彎腰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流淚", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0002", "text": "難堪深深 埋在血液裏 像個地雷", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 3, 3, 0, 2, 4, 2, 5, 2, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["naan4", "ham1", "sam1", "sam1", "maai4", "zoi6", "hyut3", "jik6", "leoi5", "zoeng6", "go3", "dei6", "leoi4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "難堪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "深深", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "埋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "血液", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地雷", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0003", "text": "懷中耿耿 無論張或退 亦似洶洶的洪水", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 9, 9, 0, 2, 3, 2, 4, 2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 0, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waai4", "zung1", "gang2", "gang2", "mou4", "leon6", "zoeng1", "waak6", "teoi3", "jik6", "ci5", "hung1", "hung1", "dik1", "hung4", "seoi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "懷中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "耿耿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無論", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "張", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "或", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "退", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "洶洶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "洪水", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0004", "text": "隨地湧起 又狠狠的過去", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 9, 9, 2, 9, 9, 3, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ceoi4", "dei6", "jung2", "hei2", "jau6", "han2", "han2", "dik1", "gwo3", "heoi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "隨地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "湧起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "狠狠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過去", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0005", "text": "每次也讓我死去活來 地老天荒非痛不可", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 5, 2, 5, 9, 4, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 4, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mui5", "ci3", "jaa5", "joeng6", "ngo5", "sei2", "heoi3", "wut6", "loi4", "dei6", "lou5", "tin1", "fong1", "fei1", "tung3", "bat1", "ho2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "每次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "死去活來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地老天荒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "非痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不可", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0006", "text": "你永遠沒法感受這痛楚 如 割去什麼", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 5, 2, 4, 9, 2, 5, 4, 9, 0, 4, 4, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "wing5", "jyun5", "mut6", "faat3", "gam2", "sau6", "ze5", "tung3", "co2", "jyu4", "got3", "heoi3", "sam6", "mo1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "永遠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒法", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感受", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痛楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "割", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0007", "text": "人間的痛楚 即使於瞬間 流過", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 4, 9, 3, 9, 3, 4, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "dik1", "tung3", "co2", "zik1", "si2", "jyu1", "seon3", "lau4", "gwo3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痛楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "即使", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "瞬間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流過", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0008", "text": "加起的痛楚 都未夠我的一半多", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 3, 4, 9, 3, 2, 4, 5, 3, 3, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gaa1", "hei2", "dik1", "tung3", "co2", "dou1", "mei6", "gau3", "ngo5", "dik1", "jat1", "bun3", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "加起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痛楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一半多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0009", "text": "長戚的痛苦難過 錐心鑽骨是神經痛", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 4, 9, 0, 4, 3, 3, 4, 3, 2, 0, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["coeng4", "tung3", "fu2", "naan4", "gwo3", "zeoi1", "sam1", "zyun3", "gwat1", "si6", "san4", "ging1", "tung3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "長戚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痛苦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錐心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鑽骨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "神經痛", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "神經痛", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1776", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MTc3Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
